<item>
            <title>[LU-11635] GSS build for client-only</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11635</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A few issues found on current master branch:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;when building client-only packages, lgssc.conf is not included, whereas this file is required on both client and server sides in order for GSS to work properly.;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;it is not possible to manually enable or disable gss support in debian packages, as corresponding options are not passed along.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I will push a patch to fix these issues.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
